  "remarks": "Viktar Luttsau is the head of the medical unit in Prison No 1 in Grodno. In this position, he is responsible for the inhumane treatment of detainees and lack of appropriate and timely medical assistance. The lack of proper medical treatment led to the death of political prisoner Ales Pushkin, who was not provided timely medical assistance.",
